00:03:12.530 --> 00:03:13.950
What are your thoughts on human composting?

00:03:13.950 --> 00:03:15.080
Would you do it?

00:03:15.080 --> 00:03:18.640
I know I would, if I didn’t already have
plans to shoot myself into space.

